              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Two podcasters, same niche. Podcaster A: Podpage, automatic RSS import, basic show notes. Podcaster B: Framer, beautiful episode pages with full transcripts, guest photos, key takeaways, SEO-optimized. Six months: Podcaster A 50 downloads/episode. Podcaster B 5000. Show notes that rank = discoverability engine.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">"Listen on Spotify" only vs embedded player + transcript - 3x engagement time</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Podcaster: "Listen on Spotify" links off platform. Added embedded player + full transcript on page. On-site engagement: 3x time on site. SEO traffic: +340%. Keep listeners on your site. Give Google content to index. Your show notes are your SEO engine.</p>
