            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Guest bio: "CEO of Company" vs "How she sold first startup for $47M" - 4x clicks</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Podcast guest bios: "John Smith, CEO of TechCorp." Changed to: "How he sold first startup for $47M, failed twice, built TechCorp to $12M ARR." Guest page clicks: 4x increase. Specific stories > generic titles. Show guests as interesting humans, not job titles.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Episode 127 vs "How to negotiate salary" in URL - 73% more search traffic</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Podcast: episode URLs "episode-127," "episode-128." Changed to URL slugs: "how-to-negotiate-salary," "battle-imposter-syndrome." Search traffic: +73%. Your URLs are SEO. Episode numbers mean nothing to Google. Topics mean everything. Make your URLs descriptive.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">No transcript vs full transcript - 4.7x more search traffic</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tested two identical podcasts. One with transcripts, one without. Transcript podcast: 4.7x more search traffic after 6 months. Google can't index audio. Transcripts turn invisible audio into searchable content. Not optional for growth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">5 Best AI Website Builders for Podcasts</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {tools.map((tool, index) => (
          <div class={`border-[3px] p-6 ${index === 0 ? 'border-violet-500 bg-violet-50' : 'border-gray-300 bg-white'}`}>
            {tool.badge && (
              <span class={`inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 ${
                index === 0 ? 'bg-violet-500 text-white' : 'bg-gray-900 text-white'
              }`}>
                {tool.badge}
              </span>
            )}
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.name}</h3>
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-violet-500">{tool.rating}</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">{tool.verdict}</p>

            <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase">Pros</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                {tool.pros.map(pro => (
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
